short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension prints exams attempts from Blackboard Learn (developed by Imtiaz Ahmad)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Google Chrome extension will help the educators to take a print (or convert to PDF using "Save as PDF" option of Chrome) of student attempt. If you do not use this extension, you will get only one page as print as visible part of current tab.
